Class SymbolTable

java.lang.Object
  vista.app.SymbolTable

public class SymbolTable
extends java.lang.Object

A hash table to assign a unique name to a given object. If the object has not been seen before it is given a new name = lowercase(object.getClass().getName()) + number_objects_of_that_type
